= DESCRIPTION

http://github.com/gdakram/JQuery-Tooltip-Plugin

= INTRODUCTION

A JQuery tooltip plugin that easily adds tooltip interaction to HTML element
that requires a bit more information than a title attribute

= USAGE

HTML
----
<div class="selector">
  Hello World
  <div class="description" style="display:none" title="Tooltip Description">
    Hello World Tooltip Description
  </div>
</div>

Javascript
----------
$("div.selector").tooltip();

